data.description: Highly sought after community in Northside Jacksonville off New Berlin. Super convenience location, minutes from I-295. New Berlin Elementary School is across the street. William F Sheffield Regional Park is next to the school. Just 2 minutes to Publix shopping center, Walmart, Medical offices, shoppes, Gate gas station, and multiple restaurants. 10 minutes to River City Marketplace! 15 minutes to Jax Airport! This magnificent home has LVP flooring throughout the house. The front and backyard has beautiful Bermuda grass! Fore! Fenced backyard, ceiling fans, irrigation system.
